+.. _OAuthAuthorizationServerDefinition:
+
+Defining authorization server
+""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
+Definitions of authorization server are added as below.
+
+* ``oauth2-auth.xml``
+
