+.. list-table::
+    :header-rows: 1
+    :widths: 10 90
+
+    * - Sr.No.
+      - Explanation
+    * - | (1)
+      - |  Bean is defined for \ ``OAuth2ClientContextFilter``\ by using \ ``<oauth2:client>``\ tag. The string specified in \ ``id``\ attribute is used as Bean ID.
